# CODEOWNERS File
# This file defines code ownership for the Nova Aetus project.
# Following quant firm best practices for clear responsibility and review requirements.
#
# Syntax: <file-pattern> <owners>
# Owners can be GitHub usernames, team names, or email addresses
# Use @username for GitHub, @org/team-name for teams

